snippet.title: The Art Collector Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Art Collector is a Cozy Roguelite Shop Keeper Sim with Tempo and RPG elements. 
Submit your in-game creations to our discord for a chance to win a copy of the game at release and to be featured in game! 
Play the Demo, Follow & Wishlist: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2986690/The_Art_Collector/
Tune in to The Art Collector OST: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DmerDt3AC58&list=PLDGsVnTVftTNWBW4SET7rkhbQAZTUMiTS&index=7&ab_channel=ShyborgGames
